{
  "stem": "25834.4",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mostly, each day I was there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because later there, like I said before, Mr.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Melamed parents has difficulty to have some representative in Aryan part for the selling the toys.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I took this part.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I sell the toys all over the Warsaw for a big supplier in other words.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The toys was produced in the ghetto from the wood.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I not think so.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Was problem with the supply of the material.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I mean the wood still was traditionally done, all the time, in this area where was ghetto.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And each third days, four days, I was sent big [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] wagon, you know, because it's light stuff, a big wagon to Warsaw, with each package, which was separate, and sent to the store.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Some store called Mr.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Birnbaum, directly called, because telephone was free.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Not free, only was possible to talk.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Some, I pick up the order and sent-- bring it to Mr.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Birnbaum.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And later there, after it was delivered to the place, I collect the money.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I bring the money to Birnbaum and to meet family, Melamed and so.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And that was-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I was almost each day in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "To be in ghetto and meet the people was fine.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Only go through the street was terrible.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Sometimes you go 100 feet, and you see 5, 6, sometimes more people dying, dying on the street.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "That was the worst part what you can see.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And the part of the-- in ghetto was organization where, you know, policemen supposed to keep the-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] in other words, keep the quiet there.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And also, on the other hand, the policemen has the obligation-- obligation from German, bring-- later there, bring 10,000 people to camp.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
